% C# Language Ontology - CNL Format
% Extends oo_ontology.cnl with C#-specific concepts
%
% This ontology maps C#-specific concepts to the generic OO ontology.
% All C# entities should use the unified CNL names with language="csharp".

% ============================================================================
% C#-Specific Entity Types
% ============================================================================

% File/Module types
Every csharp-compilation-unit is a compilation-unit.
Every csharp-namespace is a namespace.

% Type definitions
Every csharp-class is a class.
Every csharp-interface is an interface.
Every csharp-struct is a struct.
Every csharp-enum is an enum.
Every csharp-delegate is a delegate.
Every csharp-record is a class.

% Members
Every csharp-method is a method.
Every csharp-property is a property.
Every csharp-field is a field.
Every csharp-constructor is a constructor.
Every csharp-event is an event.
Every csharp-indexer is a property.

% Parameters
Every csharp-parameter is a parameter.
Every csharp-ref-parameter is a csharp-parameter.
Every csharp-out-parameter is a csharp-parameter.
Every csharp-in-parameter is a csharp-parameter.

% Import
Every csharp-using is a using.
Every csharp-using-static is a csharp-using.

% Exception handling
Every csharp-try-block is a try-block.
Every csharp-catch-clause is a catch-clause.
Every csharp-finally-clause is a finally-clause.
Every csharp-throw-statement is a throw-statement.

% Control flow
Every csharp-return-statement is a return-statement.

% Other
Every csharp-attribute is an attribute.
Every csharp-reference is a reference.
Every csharp-literal is a literal.

% ============================================================================
% C#-Specific Concepts
% ============================================================================

% Partial types
Every partial-class is a class.
Every partial-struct is a struct.
Every partial-interface is an interface.

% Static types
Every static-class is a class.

% Nested types
Every nested-class is a class.
Every nested-struct is a struct.
Every nested-interface is an interface.

% Extension methods
Every extension-method is a method.

% Async
Every async-method is a method.

% LINQ
Every linq-query is an expression.

% ============================================================================
% C# Access Modifiers (as concepts)
% ============================================================================

Every public-member is a member.
Every private-member is a member.
Every protected-member is a member.
Every internal-member is a member.
Every protected-internal-member is a member.
Every private-protected-member is a member.

% ============================================================================
% C# Exception Handling Patterns
% ============================================================================

% General catch - catches System.Exception
Every general-catch is a catch-clause.

% Empty catch - catches and does nothing
Every empty-catch is a catch-clause.

% Rethrow pattern
Every rethrow-catch is a catch-clause.

% ============================================================================
% C# Code Smells
% ============================================================================

% Magic numbers
Every magic-number-literal is a literal.

% God class
Every csharp-god-class is a god-class.

% Large method
Every csharp-long-method is a long-method.
